    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/29f125a01eed24c1eda59c33f169e93f.poster.avif?t=1749744891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/29f125a01eed24c1eda59c33f169e93f.webm?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/29f125a01eed24c1eda59c33f169e93f.mp4?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《赤痕》全新篇章，揭开黑暗史诗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在 16 世纪的英国，这里是被黑暗吞噬的诅咒之地——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入 2.5D 哥特风格的阴影世界，运筹帷幄，磨枪锉剑，在广袤的土地上展开冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/edb008eea674782d95216ef30ae5e3f4.poster.avif?t=1749744891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/edb008eea674782d95216ef30ae5e3f4.webm?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/edb008eea674782d95216ef30ae5e3f4.mp4?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国与教会屡次挥师征讨，誓要攻陷魔王埃利亚斯统治的“幻影城堡”，解救被奴役的苍生。然而每一次讨伐，皆如泥牛入海，全军覆没。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，讨伐的机会再次降临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坎坷的命运使二人在此相遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隶属于教会战斗团“黑狼团”的年轻战士：莱昂纳多·布兰顿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国骑士团“白鹿团”的最后幸存者：亚历山大·吉帝拉</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/f3ee562e240a3c1b779fb35fa0eb2ed7.poster.avif?t=1749744891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/f3ee562e240a3c1b779fb35fa0eb2ed7.webm?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/f3ee562e240a3c1b779fb35fa0eb2ed7.mp4?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们为不同的信念而战，却怀揣相同的目的：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >斩杀无形之城的统治者——魔王埃利亚斯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莱昂纳多与亚历山大的战斗之旅，就此展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/fd35b23ecb3da9b4bb275b98b01cabce.poster.avif?t=1749744891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/fd35b23ecb3da9b4bb275b98b01cabce.webm?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/fd35b23ecb3da9b4bb275b98b01cabce.mp4?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进一步深入《赤痕》的世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为《赤痕》带来黎明的全新英雄，与宿命之敌，即将登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事以细腻的笔触勾勒出深邃的世界观，搭配震撼的过场动画，将剧情推向高潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新玩家可以轻松融入故事，而老粉丝也能发现令人会心一笑的惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新功能“伙伴系统”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一次，你不再孤军奋战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与伙伴携手迎敌，智破陷阱，共赴胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索广袤无垠、充满未知的世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验《赤痕》史上最庞大的冒险舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅如此，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >晨光、烈日、暮色、月夜——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的光影也将随着时间的变化而流转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是视觉上的点缀，更是影响你与世界互动的重要元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新战斗系统“闪技”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战斗与剧情解锁全新的“闪技”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由搭配组合，打造属于你的终极战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锻造·烹饪·定制</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作新增装备外观变化要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心调整装备外观，打造独特的角色风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时，延续前作丰富的锻造与烹饪系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过多元途径，强化你的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/eb199595bcb23682f0d3af48355f01ac.poster.avif?t=1749744891\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/eb199595bcb23682f0d3af48355f01ac.webm?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883810/extras/eb199595bcb23682f0d3af48355f01ac.mp4?t=1749744891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
